<para style="p">For the chief musician; on stringed instruments. A psalm of David.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />Answer me when I call, God of my righteousness;</para>

<para style="q1">give me room when I am hemmed in.</para>

<para style="q1">Have mercy on me and listen to my prayer.</para>
